<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>결제 완료 | Seoyeon Tour</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; background: #f8f7f4; }
        .success-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            padding: 48px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 100px auto;
        }
        .check-icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: #1a1a2e;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
        }
        .check-icon svg {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            stroke: #fff;
            fill: none;
            stroke-width: 2.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-card">
        <div class="check-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="fw-medium mb-2">결제가 완료되었습니다</h4>
        <p class="text-muted small mb-4">예약이 정상적으로 처리되었습니다.</p>
        <div class="d-flex gap-2 justify-content-center">
            <a href="/mypage" class="btn btn-dark btn-sm px-4">마이페이지</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-sm px-4">홈으로</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
